$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
query_language_size

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
query_language_size -  This method returns the size of the language (used by add_read_mess()).
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
int query_language_size(string lang)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^lang%^RESET%^ - the language to get the size of
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
the size of each letter in standard handwriting
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/handlers/languages.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method returns the size of the language (used by add_read_mess()).
Some languages have bigger letters and stuff than others.
.EP

